comments: Simons (POR) is moving alongside Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Dort (OKC) extends his right arm and initiates contact to Simons' (POR) lower body which affects his SQBR during the drive.
Simons (POR) legally contests Williams' (OKC) jump shot attempt.
Brogdon (POR) goes to, not through, Joe's (OKC) space and marginal contact occurs as Brogdon (POR) releases away during the drive.
Ayton (POR) establishes himself in Joe's (OKC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Simons (POR) legally contests Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Walker (POR) establishes himself in Dort's (OKC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Simons (POR) is moving alongside Williams' (OKC) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Williams (OKC) goes to, not through, Simons's (POR) space and marginal contact occurs as Williams (OKC) releases away at the end of the drive.

Brogdon (POR) ends his dribble and gets trapped by Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) and Williams (OKC).  He thereafter dribbles again.  (An attempt to call a timeout by Coach Billups (POR) during this play is neither recognized nor granted by the officials.)
Coach Billups (POR) is assessed an unsportsmanlike technical foul for making contact with a game official.
Following the first technical foul, Coach Billups (POR) aggressively follows and pursues a game official and is assessed a second unsportsmanlike technical foul and ejected from the game.
Simons (POR) legally contests Williams' (OKC) jump shot attempt.
